tabs.tab_title: How do I create a Teamhelp account?
tabs.tab_content: To create an account, simply click on the "Sign Up" button on our homepage, fill in your details, and follow the prompts. You will receive a confirmation email to activate your account.

tabs.tab_title: How long does the onboarding process take?
tabs.tab_content: The onboarding process typically takes 1-2 days, depending on the complexity of your setup and integration needs. Our team will guide you through each step to ensure a smooth transition to Teamhelp.

tabs.tab_title: What pricing plans does Teamhelp offer?
tabs.tab_content: Teamhelp offers flexible pricing plans to suit different business sizes and needs. Our plans range from basic packages for small teams to advanced options for larger enterprises.

tabs.tab_title: Can Teamhelp integrate with other software tools?
tabs.tab_content: Yes! Teamhelp integrates seamlessly with a wide variety of tools, including CRM systems, communication platforms, and project management software.

tabs.tab_title: How can I contact support if I encounter an issue?
tabs.tab_content: You can contact our support team via email, call us directly, or use our live chat feature for real-time assistance. We're here to help 24/7.

tabs.tab_title: What should I do if I forget my password?
tabs.tab_content: If you forget your password, click on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page. You'll receive an email with instructions to reset your password.

tabs.tab_title: Can I customize the Teamhelp dashboard for my team?
tabs.tab_content: Absolutely! Teamhelp allows you to customize your dashboard to suit your team's workflow. You can rearrange modules, create custom reports, and set permissions for different team members.
